Interface IMessageTransformer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IFromMessageTransformer, IToMessageTransformer
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ISolaceMessageTransformer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultJMSTransformer, FIXMLTransformer, FixTransportTransformer, FlexibleTagTransformer, MQTransformer, OlympicRawTransformer, SocketAdapterRawTransformer, SolaceRawFIXSendingTransformer, SolaceRawTransformer, SolaceStringFIXSendingTransformer, SolaceStringTransformer, StandardFixTransformer, TechnologyAdapterFIXSendingTransformer, TIBRVNameTransformer, TIBRVRawTransformer, TIBRVTransformer

    public interface IMessageTransformer
extends IFromMessageTransformer, IToMessageTransformer
    Transformer for converting objects into IFIXMessages or IFIXMessages into objects. This class replaces the ITransformer class and uses the new IFIXMessage interface.
